---
title: Lomo Saltado-Inspired Double Steak with Aji Verde
description: Lomo saltado, hailing from the Chinese-Peruvian chifa tradition, is a glorious east-west mashup of steak night and stir fry. Our keto-style riff on this dish features juicy steak served with peppers  tossed in soy and vinegar for seriously deep, deep flavour.
